<p><strong>Medium humanoid (dwarf), lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 18 (chain mail, shield)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 39 (6d8+12)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 25 ft.</p>

